  "title": "Operations Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><p>• Update liquid loading schedules, weighing ticket/ Certificate Of Conformance</p><p>• Data entry for Delivery Order in SAP system</p><p>• Prepare GRN and stock report</p><p>• (ISO-Route Card) Liquid from VST to LGC</p><p>• Record daily LGC refilling (In & out)</p><p>• Monthly LGC movement report to Accounts for billing</p><p>• The daily record of the VST balance liquid</p><p>• Prepare monthly liquid loss report</p><p>• Good Issue (SAP)(ISO-Route Card) liquid from ISO tank to Vertical Storage Tank (VST)</p><p>• Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Preferable candidate possess at least Degree/Diploma in any fields</p></li><li><p>Strong interpersonal skills and ability to build relationships</p></li><li><p>Knowledge SAP is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently and effectively manage multiple priorities.</p></li><li><p>Monday to Friday, 8:30am to 6:00pm</p></li><li><p>Saturday, 8:30am to 12:30pm <strong>(alternate)</strong></p></li><li><p><em><strong>Singaporean only may apply</strong></em></p></li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><p>Annual Wage Supplement (AWS)</p></li><li><p>Variable Bonus</p></li><li><p>Outpatient medical </p></li></ul>",
